587
00:38:57,084 --> 00:38:58,127
I'm a good mother.

588
00:38:58,210 --> 00:39:00,463
You are a great mother,

589
00:39:00,546 --> 00:39:02,423
but you are in denial.

590
00:39:04,467 --> 00:39:05,885
What is it about this guy?

