in connection to other murders
in other states. Liz...

600
00:39:45,257 --> 00:39:47,802
You know this didn't start
with a stop sign.

601
00:39:50,221 --> 00:39:51,680
<i>Ted Bundy has been recaptured</i>

602
00:39:51,764 --> 00:39:53,933
<i>after spending nearly six days of freedom</i>

603
00:39:54,016 --> 00:39:55,476
<i>in the mountains near Aspen.</i>

604
00:39:56,310 --> 00:39:58,479
<i>This morning he was returned to court</i>

605
00:39:58,562 --> 00:40:02,358
<i>and arraigned on numerous
additional charges relating to his escape.</i>

606
00:40:09,115 --> 00:40:10,366
Let me see your hands.

607
00:40:19,583 --> 00:40:20,501
Thanks, guys.

608
00:40:22,711 --> 00:40:24,088
Oh, my gosh.

609
00:40:26,715 --> 00:40:27,591
Mmm.

610
00:40:30,428 --> 00:40:31,554
So, what do you think?

611
00:40:36,475 --> 00:40:37,852
Outside, fresh air...

612
00:40:37,935 --> 00:40:38,769
Fancy.

613
00:40:44,608 --> 00:40:45,776
Merry Christmas.

614
00:40:47,361 --> 00:40:48,446
I'm sorry, I...

615
00:40:49,238 --> 00:40:50,573
I didn't get you anything.

616
00:40:51,115 --> 00:40:54,160
You brought me the only thing I wanted
in the entire world.

617
00:40:57,455 --> 00:40:58,414
Gonna open it?

618
00:40:59,957 --> 00:41:00,875
Yeah.

619
00:41:06,922 --> 00:41:08,299
I've read it four times.

620
00:41:10,050 --> 00:41:12,261
You remember what it's about, don't you?

621
00:41:13,095 --> 00:41:14,472
Never lose hope.

622
00:41:15,347 --> 00:41:16,265
You haven't...

623
