714
00:47:47,531 --> 00:47:50,450
that will shock you
beyond your worst nightmares.

715
00:47:51,285 --> 00:47:53,912
It's only a matter of time
before the cards are on the table.

716
00:47:53,996 --> 00:47:55,622
And when they are, they will rock you.

717
00:47:56,081 --> 00:47:56,915
Is that it?

718
00:47:57,457 --> 00:48:00,460
Sooner or later, you're going to have
to confront the truth.

719
00:48:03,964 --> 00:48:05,299
For everyone's sake.

720
00:48:06,174 --> 00:48:07,134
Including yours.

721
00:48:07,801 --> 00:48:09,845
I hope it's soon. Good night.

